description:
Title : Bheemavaram Bullodu (2014)
Star Cast : Sunil , Ester Noronha,
Director : Uday Shankar
Producer : Suresh Babu
Music :Anoop Rubens

Bhimavaram Bullodu starrs Sunil and Esther in lead roles. Directed by Uday Sankar,who earlier directed Kalisundam ra.This movie is produced by Suresh Productions.Anoop Rubens Composes the music for this flick.Tanikella Bharani and JP play important roles.
